<br>
Was invited into a group in Dreadlands when I was in my low 40s.  I happened to know the enchanter that was in the group (Vergil) who I have always thought to be an excellent chanter.  In any case, the group picked up a 6th member shortly after I joined, and it was an Iksar monk named Bruze.  He was in the guild Family of Light, which happened to also be Vergil's guild.  The group hummed along nicely, pulling 2, 3 at a time as is common when you have a chanter in the group.  Well, one time the puller pulled a few too many, and the chanter kept juggling the mezzes until finally he got beat on pretty bad and proceeded to get the dreaded low health aggro and died.  Those poor chanters.  But here was the remarkable part, that I never forgot.  When Vergil got back, Bruze, who was in the same guild as Vergil, proceeded to reem out Vergil.  He told him he was a sorry enchanter and would never be any good in the 50s.  And here was his explanation:  Every good chanter roots AND mezzes the adds!!!!  <br>
<br>
Now, I've never run a chanter, so I don't know THAT much about the class, but I don't think I had ever seen chanter root and mezz adds.  In any case, the tone and language that he used with the enchanter seemed particularly harsh to me, especially considering that they were in the same guild.   <p>***  Givins, 52nd level Erudite Wizard, Rodcet Nife  ***</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/uheimdallazureguardian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heimdall Azureguardian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cons Dubious </span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#333333>(10/2/02 10:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bruze</span><hr size=1> I see a lot of Rooting ENC mez'ed adds.  Of course, I often root the mezzed adds myself too <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   So its not that unheard of.  Just don't let your druid or ranger do the rooting and its all gravy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/udiefenbakerbakendiefer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DiefenbakerBakendiefer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cons Threateningly </span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#333333>(10/5/02 3:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bruze</span><hr size=1> well bruze sucks @#%$. Anyone who thinks thier god and everyone else is a n00b needs to be shot.<br>
